insertMeasure

public static android.net.Uri insertMeasure(android.content.Context context,
                                            String sensor,
                                            String value)
                                     throws IllegalArgumentException
Insert measure with default basetime and time. Same as

Parameters:
context - the context used for the content resolver
sensor - the name of the associated sensor
value - the value of the measure
Returns:
the uri of the newly inserted measure, the measure id is -1 in case of failure
Throws:
IllegalArgumentException
See Also:
insertMeasure(Context context, String sensor, int value), insertMeasure(Context context, String sensor, float value)
